- LSGVoter.t.sol (934 lines) - 55 comprehensive tests

Key Features:
- NFT-based voting power (1 NFT = 1 vote)
- 7-day calendar-aligned epochs
- Synthetix-style index-based revenue distribution
- LSG-specific delegation mapping
- Emergency controls (pause, per-strategy kill)
- Multi-token revenue handling

Security Highlights:
- ReentrancyGuard on all state-changing functions
- SafeERC20 for all token transfers
- Access control (onlyOwner, onlyRevenueRouter, onlyEmergency)
- Input validation (zero address checks, array validation)
- Event emissions for all state changes

Test Results:
- 86 tests passing (55 LSGVoter + 31 MultiTokenRouter)
- All security-relevant scenarios tested

